RACE.RACE_TEXT: Marathon Series S. GRANDE PRAIRIE RACE 5 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 70. Claiming Stakes Purse 9000. THOROUGHBRED CLAIMING STAKES FOR THREE YEARS OLD & UPWARD. Claiming Price $4,000. Horses must have started for a Claiming Price of $5,000 or less in 2022 / 23. Horses with the highest earnings from Leg 1 will be given preference. Preference will be given to those horses that have started twice on Class B track in Alberta for 2022 / 23. Entry fee of $150 due at time of entry. All Entry Fee monies received for each of the legs of these series will be collected at time of entry. All entry fee money will be pooled together from all three legs and distributed using a points system. Only the top three horses of each series will be eligible to receive the bonus money. Point system breakdown can be found on the preference list for Evergreen Park.
